flowchart TD
    A[Device Telemetry & Network Alerts Input] --> B{Data Validation & Preprocessing}
    B -->|Valid Data| C[Feature Extraction]
    B -->|Invalid Data| Z[Return Null Threat Assessment]
    C --> D[Temporal Features<br/>Healthcare IoT Data]
    C --> E[Network Features<br/>Security Alerts]
    D --> F[LSTM Autoencoder<br/>Temporal Analysis]
    E --> G[Isolation Forest<br/>Network Analysis]
    F --> H[LSTM Results<br/>Reconstruction Errors]
    G --> I[Isolation Results<br/>Anomaly Scores]
    H --> J[Decision Fusion<br/>Adaptive Weighting]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Calculate Confidence<br/>& Threat Level]
    K --> L{Threat Level > Threshold?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Create Threat Assessment<br/>Log Detection]
    L -->|No| N[Return Null Assessment<br/>Below Threshold]
    M --> O[Output: Threat Assessment<br/>& Confidence Score]
    N --> P[Output: No Threat Detected]
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style F fill:#fff3e0
    style G fill:#f3e5f5
    style J fill:#e8f5e8
    style O fill:#ffebee
    style P fill:#f1f8e9
